text: J-Town can refer to a number of things, including: * A contraction of Jerusalem * A contraction of Japantown * A nickname given to Joliet, Illinois by residents * A nickname for Japantown, in San Francisco, California * A nickname given to Ciudad Juárez * A nickname for Jeffersontown, Kentucky * A nickname for Jacksonville, Florida * A nickname for Jakarta, Indonesia * A nickname for Jászfényszaru, Hungary (used by foreigners, because it is difficult to pronounce the town's native name by most foreigners) * A nickname for Jos, Nigeria * A nickname for Jülich, Germany * A nickname for Jeddah, Saudi Arabia
title: J-Town
